        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1467697890" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18111275171482084141">I was fascinated at first but then he mixed too many timelines and characters without any purpose and relied on sex too much so i totally lost interest. A weird book like an experiment but maybe one needs to be under drugs to appreciate it as the writer wrote it.</span>

          </span>
